            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Host-parasite associations in a population of the nectarivorous bat Anoura geoffroyi (Phyllostomidae) in a cave in a Brazilian ferruginous geosystem",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Luísa Lauren Lima",
                    "lastName": "Vidal"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
